      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exemplary caliber, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Its provenance and aesthetic integrity make it a premier acquisition for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite serious inquiries to experience this benchmark of quality firsthand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
